---
description: Localization rules for package.json contributed settings
globs: package.json,package.nls*.json
alwaysApply: false
---

# Contributed Settings (package.json)

- Use localization tokens for setting descriptions: `"%param.paramName%"`.
- Add the string to all `package.nls*.json` files (en, zh-cn, pt, ru, es, etc.).
- Never hardcode raw English strings in `package.json` for contributed settings.

```json
// ❌ Avoid
"description": "Explicitly mark this folder as an ESP-IDF project."

// ✅ Prefer
"description": "%param.extensionActivationMode%"
```

